    <item>
      <title>迪士尼在先锋集团的支持下扩大了特里安代理战的领先优势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/disney-ahead-in-trian-proxy-fight-with-most-of-votes-counted</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，在与纳尔逊·佩尔茨 (Nelson Peltz) 的特里安基金管理公司 (Trian Fund Management) 的代理权争夺战中，华特迪士尼公司 (Walt Disney Co.) 的管理层以超过 60% 的选票领先。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/disney-ahead-in-trian-proxy-fight-with-most-of-votes-counted</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 20:41:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>私营企业指数基金让支持独角兽变得更容易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/index-fund-for-private-firms-makes-it-easier-to-bet-on-unicorns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[希望利用私营公司增长的合格投资者现在有办法简化支持哪些独角兽的困境。有一个指数基金可以做到这一点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/index-fund-for-private-firms-makes-it-easier-to-bet-on-unicorns</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 18:50:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
